    "body": "Panache is a language server (formatter, and linter) for Markdown, Quarto, and R Markdown. It's built in Rust and uses a lossless CST parser. It supports integrating external formatters and linters. It's packaged at crates.io, AUR, NixOS, NPM, PyPi, and as a VSIX extension at VS Code Marketplace and Open VSX. Binaries are provided directly from the GitHub repo.\r\n\r\nLinks:\r\n\r\n- <https://panache.bz>\r\n- <https://github.com/jolars/panache>",
